                        <h1>Aaron Wagner And Wags Capital: From Pro Football To Utah&#8217;s Latest Disgraced Financial Influencer</h1>
                        <hr class="small">
                        <span class="meta"><span class="posted-on">Published on <time class="entry-date published" datetime="2024-10-28T07:13:26-05:00">October 28, 2024</time><time class="updated" datetime="2024-10-28T15:01:04-05:00">October 28, 2024</time></span></span>
